Oricorio (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0740: Crabominable
Pokémon
#0742: Cutiefly →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Oricorio (TCG Pocket).

Oricorio has been featured on 14 different cards since it debuted in the Guardians Rising expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Oricorio cards are normally Fire-type, Lightning-type, or Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Oricorio

Oricorio
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
